@NODE "MEGASTYLE" "About Megastyle"

                                                               @{" Go back.. " Link MAIN}

Megastyle is a new AmiExpress-Support group formed by Lizard of Spaceballs in
the middle of may 1995.

Our main goal is to support all the /X-boards out there with the best doors
around. We try hard to make our products as system-friendly as possible and
with unique configuration possibilities.


We want to be the leading /X-development group in the future, and therefore
need more skilled coders and ANSI-artist to make our products even better!

If you're interesting in teaming up, then take a look at the contact-info.



